targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  time_index AS "time",
  availablespotnumber AS "availablespotnumber",
  longitude(location_centroid) AS "longitude",
  latitude(location_centroid) AS "latitude",
  entity_id,
  time_index,
  entity_type,
  location
FROM doc.example
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time_index) AND
  entity_type = 'OffStreetParking'
ORDER BY 1
